txt.en: 'The towers stand, but I do not trust them. Wood does not burn like this town did and still hold weight. If we repair them, we gain the ability to see when the Enemy is coming and have our archers be able to loose upon them as they crash against our palisades.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
Bring the Tokens of Hytbold to Warin
